# AI Inventory Demand Forecasting System (XGBoost + Flask)

An end-to-end machine learning system covering data processing, feature engineering, model training, evaluation, and deployment.

A machine learning web application that predicts daily inventory demand using historical sales patterns.  
Built as a final-year dissertation project focused on improving inventory management for SMEs.

---

## Project Overview

Small and Medium-Sized Enterprises (SMEs) often struggle with inventory management due to:
- Limited resources
- Poor demand forecasting
- Disconnected data systems

This project demonstrates how **AI-driven forecasting** can improve decision-making by:
- Predicting daily sales demand
- Reducing stockouts and overstocking
- Enabling data-driven inventory planning

---
##  Dissertation Context

This project was developed as part of my final-year dissertation, focusing on the application of machine learning techniques to improve inventory demand forecasting for Small and Medium-Sized Enterprises (SMEs).

The research explored how data-driven forecasting models can support better stock management decisions, reduce waste, and improve operational efficiency.

---
## Model & Approach

- Model: **XGBoost Regressor**
- Dataset: Retail demand dataset (~9 million records)
- Features:
  - Date-based (day, month, weekday, weekend)
  - Aggregated statistics:
    - Store average sales
    - Item average sales
    - Store-item interactions
    - Day-of-week trends

---
##  Methodology

The project followed a structured machine learning pipeline:

1. Data preprocessing and cleaning  
2. Feature engineering (date-based and aggregated features)  
3. Model training using XGBoost  
4. Hyperparameter tuning with RandomizedSearchCV  
5. Model evaluation using RMSE and MAPE  
6. Deployment via a Flask web application  

This approach ensured both strong predictive performance and practical usability.
---
## Model Performance

| Metric     | Value   |
|-----------|--------|
| RMSE      | 7.25   |
| MAPE      | 13.11% |
| Accuracy  | 86.89% |

