## Installation & Setup

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Haadii-dev/AI-Inventory-Demand-Forecasting-System-XGBoost-Flask-
cd inventory-forecast
```
### Install dependencies:
```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```
### Run the app:
```
python app.py
```
### Open in browser:
```
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```
---
## API Usage
### Endpoint
``` bash
POST /predict
```
### Example Request
```JSON
{
  "store": 1,
  "item": 1,
  "date": "2017-04-10"
}
```
### Example Response
```JSON
{
  "store": 1,
  "item": 1,
  "date": "2017-04-10",
  "predicted_sales": 13.42
}
```

### Health Check
```bash
GET /health
```
